== Padrino Content Model Template ==

A template for generating Padrino apps with an ActiveRecord Content model which can be used to create pages, snippets (page fragments) and components (menus, navs, footers). Currently bundled with CKEditor to make content editing a bit easier.

Usage: padrino g project my_project --template path/to/cms_template.rb

